  "title": "Facilities Management Executive",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities</p><p></p><p>Facilities Operations & Maintenance</p><p>•\tConduct daily inspections of common areas, facilities, and equipment</p><p>•\tMonitor cleanliness, lighting, lifts, plumbing, electrical systems, and amenities</p><p>•\tReport and follow up on defects, breakdowns, or safety hazards</p><p>•\tCoordinate preventive and corrective maintenance works</p><p></p><p>Vendor & Contractor Coordination</p><p>•\tLiaise with service providers (cleaners, lift contractors, landscapers, pest control, etc.)</p><p>•\tSupervise on-site works and ensure compliance with safety and work procedures</p><p>•\tVerify job completion and report issues to the Managing Agent (MA)</p><p></p><p>Resident / Tenant Support</p><p>•\tAttend to residents’ feedback, complaints, and service requests</p><p>•\tExplain house rules, facility usage, and safety guidelines</p><p>Safety, Security & Compliance</p><p>•\tConduct basic safety checks and assist during emergencies</p><p>Administration & Reporting</p><p>•\tUpdate maintenance records and handover notes</p><p>•\tAssist MA with notices, facility bookings, and operational matters</p>",
