    "description": "<p>Founded in 1999, Security Enforcer is a licensed security agency with 21 years of vast professional experience in the Security industry. We provide security personnel services, coupled with advanced technological security devices to secure effectively, through Enforcement. Our clients are esteemed organizations, condominiums as well as commercial properties.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We value each and every employee as our family, forming a close knitted company that we can all thrive in. We look forward to welcome you into our big family of happy employees and security personnel.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to &lt;hrjennyteo@securityenforcer.com.sg&gt; stating your contact details, work experiences and date of availability.</p>",
